  <TITLE>Use PayPal .NET SDK</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>This Classic SDK is not actively supported and will be deprecated in the future. Official source: https://github.com/paypal/merchant-sdk-dotnet . So it will be better if we start using PayPal .NET SDK. for Paypal Direct Payment plugin. They have proper documentation also. https://devtools-paypal.com/guide/pay_creditcard/dotnet?interactive=ON&amp;env=sandbox https://developer.paypal.com/docs/api/ So we need to uninstall existing PayPal third-party libraries and use &quot;PayPal&quot; one - https://www.nuget.org/packages/PayPal/ Sample code - https://github.com/paypal/PayPal-NET-SDK/tree/master/Samples Source: http://www.nopcommerce.com/boards/t/38848/nopcommerce-380-roadmap-and-estimated-release-date-lets-discuss.aspx?p=5#159462</DESCRIPTION>
